{# Labour / Employment Agreement Template - English | Based on tier2 template corpus #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Employment / Labour Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; margin: 40px; color: #222; }
        .header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px double #000; padding-bottom: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .intro { font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify; }
        .clause { margin: 14px 0; font-size: 11px; }
        .clause-no { font-weight: bold; min-width: 28px; display: inline-block; }
        .parties-box { border: 1px solid #888; padding: 14px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 11px; background: #fafafa; }
        .parties-box p { margin: 5px 0; }
        .signature-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 60px; }
        .sig-block { width: 44%; text-align: center; }
        .sig-line { border-top: 1px solid #000; padding-top: 4px; font-size: 11px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .witness-row { display: flex; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px; }
        .witness-block { flex: 1; }
        .disclaimer { font-size: 9px; border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; background: #fffacd; margin-top: 28px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>Employment / Labour Contract Agreement</h1>
    <p style="font-size:11px; margin-top:4px;">Under the Factories Act, 1948 &amp; Contract Labour (Regulation and Abolition) Act, 1970</p>
</div>

<div class="intro">
    <p>THIS AGREEMENT is made on the <strong>{{ agreement_date }}</strong> day of <strong>{{ agreement_month }}</strong>, <strong>{{ agreement_year }}</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top:10px;"><strong>BETWEEN:</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="parties-box">
    <p><strong>EMPLOYER:</strong></p>
    <p>{{ employer_name }}, aged {{ employer_age }} years, {{ employer_designation }},</p>
    <p>{{ employer_company }}, having its office at {{ employer_address }}</p>
    <p>(hereinafter called the <strong>"Employer"</strong>) of the ONE PART;</p>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;"><strong>AND</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top:12px;"><strong>EMPLOYEE / WORKMAN:</strong></p>
    <p>{{ employee_name }}, aged {{ employee_age }} years, S/o D/o {{ employee_parent }},</p>
    <p>residing at {{ employee_address }}</p>
    <p>(hereinafter called the <strong>"Employee"</strong>) of the OTHER PART.</p>
</div>

<p style="font-size:12px;"><strong>NOW IT IS AGREED BY AND BETWEEN THE PARTIES AS FOLLOWS:</strong></p>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">1.</span>
    <strong>Appointment &amp; Designation:</strong> The Employer hereby appoints the Employee as <strong>{{ employee_designation }}</strong> to render services as are usual and customary for such position, effective from {{ start_date }}.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">2.</span>
    <strong>Remuneration:</strong> In consideration of the services rendered, the Employer shall pay the Employee a monthly salary of <strong>Rs. {{ monthly_salary }}/- (Rupees {{ salary_in_words }} only)</strong>, payable on or before the {{ salary_day }} day of each succeeding month, so long as the Employee shall faithfully, honestly and diligently observe and perform the terms of this Agreement.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">3.</span>
    <strong>Duties and Responsibilities:</strong> The Employee shall faithfully serve the Employer and shall do and perform all work with care, punctuality, and ability as the Employer may require. The Employee shall conduct himself/herself honestly and properly towards the Employer, customers, and fellow employees at all times.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">4.</span>
    <strong>Working Hours:</strong> The Employee shall work {{ working_hours }} hours per day, {{ working_days }} days per week, as per the schedule determined by the Employer, subject to the provisions of applicable labour laws.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">5.</span>
    <strong>Leave Entitlement:</strong> The Employee shall be entitled to {{ annual_leave }} days of earned leave, {{ sick_leave }} days of sick leave, and {{ casual_leave }} days of casual leave per year, as per applicable law.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">6.</span>
    <strong>Non-Compete / Confidentiality:</strong> The Employee shall not enter the service or employment of any other person or body of persons carrying on a similar business during the continuance of this Agreement, or for a period of {{ non_compete_period }} years thereafter, without the prior written consent of the Employer.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">7.</span>
    <strong>Termination:</strong> If the Employee absents himself/herself from service without leave, is guilty of misconduct, or commits any breach of this Agreement, the Employer may, at his/her option, terminate the Employee's service without notice. In any other case, either party may terminate this Agreement by giving {{ notice_period }} days' prior notice in writing.
</div>

<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">8.</span>
    <strong>Incapacity:</strong> If the Employee is incapacitated by illness, accident, or any other cause and cannot perform his/her duties, the Employer may grant leave with or without pay, or terminate services. Compensation for injuries arising out of employment shall be governed by the Employees' Compensation Act, 1923.
</div>

{% if additional_clauses %}
<div class="clause">
    <span class="clause-no">9.</span>
    <strong>Additional Terms:</strong><br>
    <p style="white-space: pre-wrap; margin-left:28px;">{{ additional_clauses }}</p>
</div>
{% endif %}

<div class="clause" style="margin-top:20px;">
    <strong>IN WITNESS WHEREOF</strong> the parties hereto have signed this Agreement at {{ agreement_place }} on the day and year first above written.
</div>

<div class="signature-row">
    <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="sig-line">
            {{ employer_name }}<br>
            (Employer / Authorized Signatory)
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sig-block">
        <div class="sig-line">
            {{ employee_name }}<br>
            (Employee)
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="witness-row">
    <div class="witness-block">
        <p style="font-size:11px;"><strong>Witness 1:</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Name: _________________________</p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Address: _______________________</p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Signature: _____________________</p>
    </div>
    <div class="witness-block">
        <p style="font-size:11px;"><strong>Witness 2:</strong></p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Name: _________________________</p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Address: _______________________</p>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">Signature: _____________________</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <strong>⚠ DISCLAIMER:</strong> This agreement template is based on the Contract Labour (Regulation and Abolition) Act, 1970
    and general Indian labour law principles. This is NOT legal advice. Employment terms vary by state and industry.
    Please have this agreement reviewed by a qualified lawyer before execution.
    LegalSarthi assumes no liability for use of this template.
</div>

</body>
</html>
